fulltitle: Kerry Committee Report on BCCI Investigation
title: Kerry Committee Report on BCCI Investigation
tags: Bank of Credit and Commerce International
description:
For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub

Members of the Senate Foreign Relations Subcommittee on Terrorism, Narcotics and International Operations spoke in a news conference to announce the release of their report on the investigation into the Bank of Credit and Commerce International. The investigation included BCCI’s involvement with the Noriega administration in Panama and allegations of fraud and money laundering.
